<plot>In 1977, a phenomenon occurred. A new film gained such passionate fans, that 3 years later they lined up early in anticipation of the release of its sequel. That film was "Star Wars," and it's a tradition that continues to this day. "How To Stand In Line For Star Wars" is a humorous look behind the fans who line up early for "Star Wars," and more importantly, provides you with their 10 tips for a successful wait when the next chapter is released.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?248739</url></doc>
